text: Moritz Neumann (born 25 February 2005) is an Austrian footballer. He plays as a forward for Austrian Second League club FC Liefering. He also plays for the U18 Academy team of FC Red Bull Salzburg. ==Career== He started his career with SVg Mayrhofen then he went on to SV Innsbruck. 2019 he went on to the FC Red Bull Salzburg Academy.
